Resident Evil 7, MGS5 Designer Joins Nintendo EPD<br />
<br />
Jordan Amaro; game designer who was a level designer on Resident Evil 7 for Capcom, and,P.T. and Metal Gear Solid 5 for Kojima Productions - has joined Nintendo EPD (Kyoto section). Amaro has apparently been working at the company since around January-February, and is apparently helping design a Switch game that hasn't been announced yet (or maybe it's the Zelda DLC).&nbsp;
